</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
HILLARY-INTERVIEW (Washington) _ A story will move at 9 p.m. CDT,
Sunday. By CRAGG HINES. Questions, call Jake Doherty at
713-220-7674.
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
Houston Chronicle
</P>
</TEXT>
