<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-U.S.-U.N.-RELATIONS-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   U.S.-U.N.-RELATIONS (United Nations) will not move in tonight's
New York Times News Service file. It did not make Page One and is
being held for another day.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Aug. 1.
